      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ADHANA MARTINA (2) is a last start placegetter in Grade 6 company, jumping from this box and finishing a 4 length third over 530m at Murray Bridge. Has a very honest record from this same draw, including a win and three minors. Deserves another chance. TRUST DEED (6) finished fourth last time but just a few runs back pushed the clock when winning over 400m at this track, taking a Other in a slick 23.13. Has the ability and looks a key chance. PRETTY ESMAY (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (20.21) in a TG1-4W at Angle Park. Should be about the money. THUNDERING LADY (4) deserves plenty of thought at his first run at this distance.",
